Author: ComputerGenie 👴🏼📢#7004
Content:
Fun fact:
When the pseudo USD for KMD is $0.994
0.207083 KMD for 1 PIRATE
holds the same value as
when the pseudo USD for KMD was $1.20
and the trading rate was
0.25 KMD for 1 PIRATE.
So, while KMD has fallen 17%, PIRATE has fallen 32% (given a 1:0.17 trade ratio) --- not counting the *additional* pseudo USD loss PIRATE suffers after the conversion.
